_:N52ed18dd7bbc4d4aa53a8ed8023cf5f5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Anna McMorrin was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Wales Office on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Cardiff North in June 2017.</p>\n" .
